name: TestQ5
cases: SELECT n_name, SUM(ol_amount) AS revenue FROM customer, orders, order_line, stock, supplier, nation, region WHERE c_id = o_c_id AND c_w_id = o_w_id AND c_d_id = o_d_id AND ol_o_id = o_id AND ol_w_id = o_w_id AND ol_d_id = o_d_id AND ol_w_id = s_w_id AND ol_i_id = s_i_id AND MOD((s_w_id * s_i_id), 10000) = s_suppkey AND ASCII(SUBSTR(c_state, 1, 1)) - 65 = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey AND r_name = 'EUROPE' AND o_entry_d >= '2007-01-02 00:00:00.000000' GROUP BY n_name;
